## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **luspatercept Reblozyl 2019** = first FDA β-thal TDT (BELIEVE). TGF-β SMAD2/3 ligand trap → late-stage erythroid maturation 회복. β-thal TDT transfusion 부담 감소 임상 paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 ActR2B/A 가 sotatercept (cross-pulm PAH) 와 mechanism 동일.
2. **mitapivat Pyrukynd 2024 β-thal NTDT (ENERGIZE)** = first FDA β-thal NTDT. PK activator allosteric — glycolysis flux + ATP + 2,3-BPG modulation. 2022 PKD 후 NTDT 적응증 확장. quantum-VQE 의 PK allosteric pocket fit.
3. **exa-cel Casgevy 2023** = first FDA ex-vivo CRISPR β-thal TDT + SCD. BCL11A erythroid enhancer disruption → fetal Hb induction. autologous HSCT + edit. cure paradigm — 만성 transfusion 50+ year era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 BCL11A enhancer DNA-protein interface 가 직접 fit.
4. **betibeglogene autotemcel Zynteglo 2022** = first FDA ex-vivo lentivirus β-thal TDT. HGB-204 + HGB-207 trial. β^A-T87Q variant β-globin. autologous HSCT + lentivirus edit. cure paradigm 시초.
5. **bluebird bio Skysona + Lyfgenia + Zynteglo EU 철수 2022** = paradigm lessons. price + reimbursement + manufacturing scale issue. cure 가 가능해도 access 가 한정. K-식약처 framework 반영 필요.
6. **deferoxamine 1968 + deferasirox 2005 + deferiprone 2011** = iron chelation 50+ year evolution. SC 14h infusion → oral once-daily. compliance 향상 + endocrinopathies + cardiomyopathy 감소.
7. **HSCT allogeneic matched sibling** = thalassemia 만성 cure paradigm pre-2022. <17세 + matched sibling 시 90%+ 치료. GvHD 위험 + match donor 한정 = ex-vivo CRISPR/lentivirus 의 alternative.
8. **fetal Hb induction (hydroxyurea + decitabine + butyrate)** = pharmacologic HbF induction. α-thal + Hb H + β-thal NTDT 광범위 적응 가능 — research stage. BCL11A enhancer 의 분자 mechanism 보다 적은 효율.
9. **prenatal genetic testing α + β-globin + carrier screening** = preventive disease management. 한국 + 동남아 + 지중해 + 중동 carrier 빈도 높음. ELSI + 윤리 (cross-women_obgyn + preventive + pediatric_rare).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, thalassemia 만성 transfusion + chelation + cure paradigm 임상 의미 한정.

